			<p><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;<wbr>
&nbsp;<wbr></SPAN><a HREF="http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0018UpFczy7xqA2jirK08" TARGET="_blank"><img src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src ="http://s9.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0018UpFczy7xqA2jirK08&amp;690" WIDTH="690" HEIGHT="471" NAME="image_operate_43141569847585771"  ALT="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读"  TITLE="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读" /></A></P>
<p><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;<wbr>
&nbsp;<wbr> &nbsp;<wbr> &nbsp;<wbr>
&nbsp;<wbr> &nbsp;<wbr> &nbsp;<wbr>
&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<wbr></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
曾先后突破“</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒大关”的苏炳添和谢震业双双“落选”男子</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米跑决赛，让很多翘首以盼、充满期待的国人非常失望，但我却看到的是另一番景象。苏炳添跑进</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">2015</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年北京田径世锦赛、</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">2017</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年伦敦田径世锦赛时，八（九）条跑道上除了他之外全是黑人运动员。今天凌晨在卡塔尔，世锦赛男子</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米决赛的跑道上还是</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">7</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">个黑人运动员，唯一的“例外”由黄种人苏炳添换成了意大利白人托尔图。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
在中国三名女子短跑运动员韦永丽、梁小静、葛曼棋亦“遗憾”的</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米半决赛出局后，曾经的世界女子</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">200</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米霸主、荷兰白人“女飞人”斯皮尔斯也没能进入</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米决赛，最后决赛的</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">8</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">名选手是清一色的黑人。这已是近</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">40</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年世界田径一个“八九不离十”的规律，世锦赛、奥运会的男子（女子）</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米（</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">200</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米）决赛前八名跑道上，要不偶尔有一个白人、或黄种人运动员，要不就全是黑人运动员。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
这就是田径场上的肤色分界。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
这个分界在男子</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米跑道上很长时间以来也曾是以一个成绩——“</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒大关”来体现的：除黑人外，没有白人、黄种人跑进过</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">00</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
苏炳添、谢震业先后突破“</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒大关”后，日本几名短跑选手（至少包括一个黑人混血运动员）也相继突破、接近了“</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒大关”。不少人也注意到，今天凌晨获得男子</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米第</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">8</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">名的意大利白人选手托尔图虽是唯一一个成绩在</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">00</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">之外者，他的个人最好成绩也曾跑出过</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">9</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">99</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">。据说，另有一名法国白人短跑选手也曾跑进过</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">00</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
“</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">10</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒大关”的分界线不复存在，但肤色分界依然清晰可见。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><a HREF="http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0018UpFczy7xqAw0iPE4a" TARGET="_blank"><img src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src ="http://s11.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0018UpFczy7xqAw0iPE4a&amp;690" WIDTH="550" HEIGHT="393" NAME="image_operate_68821569847479073"  ALT="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读"  TITLE="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读" /></A><br />
<br /></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
为什么不是身高分界，体重、胖瘦分界，甚至不是训练是否科学、刻苦分界，而只是肤色分界？</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
因为身高、体重、胖瘦都分不出界来，因为肤色分界远不止是皮肤的颜色，而是不同肤色背后的不同运动天赋。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
据研究表明，有一系列“天生”外在和内在形状和内分泌的不同决定了</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">不同肤色、不同人种</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">后天运动成绩的优劣。外型如黑人头小、髋窄、臀高、手臂腿长，奔跑阻力更小，更接近流线型；内在如黑人婴儿肌肉、骨骼发育更早、更强，出生</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt;">9</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">小时脖子即可直立，站立、走路和奔跑时间更早，最重要的是，黑人体内荷尔蒙含量比白人、黄种人高出</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt;">2%</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">——</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt;">19%</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">（白人接近</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt;">2%</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">一端，黄种人接近</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt;">19%</SPAN><span STYLE="text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">一端），几乎等于天生服用了兴奋剂。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">30</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">岁的苏炳添没进决赛被总结为腰受伤、已过巅峰，</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">24</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">岁的谢震业呢？起跑稍慢、后程被带乱了步伐……有没有人说他俩训练不刻苦、教练不行？所有这些原因都不如“肤色分界”背后不同天赋这一个原因。若把起跑、途中跑、后程，身体条件，训练手段、时间等相关因素按比例排列，黑人运动员的天赋比例大约多出</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">20%</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，苏炳添、谢震业……及白人运动员的训练再刻苦也无法超越约</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">20%</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">的天赋差异。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
若明天凌晨谢震业跑进</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">20</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">00</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，跻身</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">200</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米决赛、甚至夺得奖牌，那将是人类田径史上的一大突破和奇迹，即：后天努力可极大缩小天赋上的差异，也是一种追求平等的奇迹。若没能跻身决赛，也属非常正常。谢震业、苏炳添已经是黄种人中最棒的，他们都已极大提升了黄种人的极限。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
田径中所有径赛中只有</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">110</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米栏、</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">400</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米和</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">400</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米栏略有例外，除此，100米、200米跑为欧美黑人所垄断，</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">800</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米以上的长距离一直到马拉松则是非洲黑人运动员的一统天下，其中以东非高原肯尼亚、埃塞俄比亚几乎包揽前三名、甚至前六名为明显特征。肯尼亚以一个非洲小国，经常能在奥运会的田径比赛和田径世锦赛上，以仅靠男女</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">800</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米以上长距离奔跑项目的好成绩，就能名列金牌榜前列（本届卡塔尔世锦赛仍将如此？）。但相比于高原的次相关因素，以上提到的内外因天赋为主相关因素。有人因这两个国家运动员的成绩好，误认为是他们拥有先进的训练手段和地理优势而派队员去那训练，实在是个天大的笑话。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">110</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米栏、</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">400</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米栏有“例外”是因为跨栏有很多后天技术，只是跑</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">110</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米刘翔肯定进不了世界前</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">50</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，但有了精确的后天栏上技术，就极大的弥补了先天奔跑上的差距。所以中国一直有崔麟、李彤等世界前八选手，当然像刘翔那样夺得奥运会、世锦赛冠军，创世界纪录，则多少是个奇迹，属几十年、一百年才出一个。</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">400</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米栏最近涌现出一个挪威白人新秀沃尔霍姆，虽然仍他属八条跑道上为数不多的白人选手，但他</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">46</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">92</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">有史以来第二好成绩，距美国选手凯文杨</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">1992</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年巴塞罗那奥运会上创下的</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">46</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">78</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">世界纪录只有咫尺之遥。男子</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">400</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米世界纪录是美国黑人选手“阿甘”迈克尔</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">.</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">约翰逊保持的</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">43</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">18</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，一个很可能保持到下世纪的纪录（最新纪录是南非运动员范凯尔克的43秒03），但一直有白人选手世界大赛夺冠，而且眼下还有个比利时三胞胎比尔利兄弟，有俩人成绩在</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">44</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">秒</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">50</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">左右，经常进入世界大赛决赛前八。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><a HREF="http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0018UpFczy7xqAloI6x55" TARGET="_blank"><img src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src ="http://s6.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0018UpFczy7xqAloI6x55&amp;690" WIDTH="550" HEIGHT="366" NAME="image_operate_47001569847533585"  ALT="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读"  TITLE="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读" /></A><br />
<br /></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
田径田赛中的跳跃，黑人也占有明显优势，虽不如跑道上那么明显。今天凌晨结束的男子三级跳，两名中国选手进入决赛，但都没过</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">17</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米，前</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">6</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">名皆为黑人选手，两位中国选手在助跑速度、弹跳和力量上与黑人运动员皆有明显差距。中国男子三跳（跳高、跳远、三级跳）在世界上一直有一席之地，近年尤其是跳远成绩比较稳定，经常有</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">3</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">人跻身前</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">12</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">名决赛的“盛况”。但</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">8</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">30</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">左右的黄种人极限，与黑人选手大赛夺冠</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">8</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">50</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">、</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">60</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">、</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">70</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">的差距，就是不同人种间不同天赋的差距。男子跳高一直是“肤色最多元化”的田径项目，虽现世界纪录是古巴黑人运动员索托马约尔所创、遥不可及的</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">2</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">米</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">45</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，但大赛决赛经常是白人、黄种人、黑人运动员“三足鼎立”，女子跳高则几乎清一色的属白人选手天下。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
但黑人运动员亦非在所有田径项目中皆有得天独厚的天赋，有时手臂长、腿长，髋窄、臀高，重心高的优势，也会变成劣势。比如投掷，男女标枪、链球赛场上就几乎看不到黑人选手。铅球、铁饼赛场上偶尔有黑人选手，但很少，比例与跑道上的白人、黄种人选手相近。原因也很简单，黑人有最好的肌肉、力量，但重心太高，投掷严重缺乏反作用力。举重赛场上几乎见不到黑人运动员也是同样的道理。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
一个最有意思的项目是撑杆跳。撑杆跳需要速度、力量，重心高若非优势，但也绝不是劣势，但为什么男女撑杆跳，世界大赛经常一个黑人都看不到？因为撑杆跳持杆助跑部分比较简单，只需跑的快、有力量（持杆），但起跳后的倒立、转体、推杆、过杆的连串动作很像体操，动作太复杂，需要大脑快速反应、严谨、精确，甚至还有计算，而这是黑人选手的劣势，需要记得动作要领太多。黑人运动员撑杆跳不行，与黑人运动员体操不行同理。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
纵观一百多年的现代奥运会及田径比赛历史，黑人（男子）运动员得天独厚的天赋是从</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">1936</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年柏林奥运会美国运动员欧文斯一人独得四枚金牌开始显露的，那之后黑人运动员在大部分田径项目上逐渐形成了垄断。而黑人女子运动员因种种社会原因，只是近年来才取代曾经风光一时的前苏联、东欧运动员，也在跑跳项目上形成了垄断。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
在本届卡塔尔田径世锦赛剩下几天的比赛中，各项目比赛的发展趋势，仍将按清晰的肤色分界进行，偶有例外，但大致如此。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
不是说“上帝是公平”的吗？为什么田径场上竟然如此的“不公平”？</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
但如果你把体力和智力放在一起看，就“公平”的多了。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
几个月前，美国一个名叫詹姆斯</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">.</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">沃特森的诺贝尔生物学奖获得者因一番不同肤色人群智商差异的言论引发争论。沃特森因发现人类的遗传物质</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">DNA</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">而夺得诺贝尔奖，他从遗传的角度提出了三大人种最基本的智商差异：东亚黄种人</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">105</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，白人</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">100</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，黑人</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size: 12.0pt">87</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">，而这个智商差异的顺序，正好与田径场上的天赋差异相反，呈现出一种完美的“对称”。体育天赋最好的，智力天赋最差；智力天赋最好的，体育天赋最差；体育天赋次最好的，智力天赋亦次最好之。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
天赋差距有时很难逾越，但后天努力可极大缩小之。人生而平等，非生下来什么都一样，而是各有所长，需互相对照、学习、弥补，去争取平等。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><a HREF="http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/0018UpFczy7xqAkCxzPc1" TARGET="_blank"><img src="http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/common/sg_trans.gif" real_src ="http://s2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0018UpFczy7xqAkCxzPc1&amp;690" WIDTH="690" HEIGHT="1060" NAME="image_operate_35451569847582480"  ALT="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读"  TITLE="田径场上的肤色分界&mdash;&mdash;卡塔尔田径世锦赛的另类解读" /></A><br />
<br /></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
最后说句题外话，体育天赋可奥运会、NBA、拳击、橄榄球、田径赛场上脱颖而出，争金夺银，智力天赋有什么用？</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
当然有！智力天赋可在智力奥运会上脱颖而出，争金夺银。数学的奥数，科学的诺贝尔奖皆为智力奥运会。还有</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">GDP</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">也是，中国近</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">40</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt;font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">年经济的高速发展，日本二战后的经济奇迹，韩国、香港、台湾、新加坡“亚洲四小龙”的崛起，其背后之唯一主因，平均</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">105</SPAN><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">的智商也。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt; font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin">
以此角度来看卡塔尔田径世锦赛，你是不是就不会因中国运动员的失误、成绩不尽如人意而扼腕叹息、抱怨他们太不争气？是不是他们以最差之天赋挑战最强天赋、只要超越了自我就会成为你的偶像？田径世锦赛进入决赛、甚至夺牌之意义，不仅不比中国人黄种人天赋最强的乒乓球、羽毛球、跳水、女子举重、射击之夺金如囊中取物的金牌差，甚至还远胜之而无不及。是不是你会更好的看懂了田径和田径世锦赛。</SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="text-indent:24.0pt"><span STYLE="font-size:12.0pt">&nbsp;<wbr></SPAN></P>							
		</div>
